00:38:15,930 --> 00:38:17,260
It's a bathhouse.

893
00:38:17,260 --> 00:38:18,460
You shouldn't go with us.

894
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:21,100
I'm not going.

895
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:34,740
You two, don't make trouble.

896
00:38:36,100 --> 00:38:36,940
Got it.

897
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:47,700
(Ninghai Public Security Bureau)

898
00:38:53,020 --> 00:38:53,860
Mr. Xing,

899
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:55,100
it's not good.

900
00:38:55,380 --> 00:38:57,220
Mr. Zhou applied for traffic control.

901
00:38:57,570 --> 00:38:58,740
It's not Binjiang.

902
00:38:58,860 --> 00:39:00,220
Many small paths don't have cameras.

903
00:39:01,150 --> 00:39:02,660
We can only speculate about

904
00:39:02,660 --> 00:39:03,860
his escape route.

905
00:39:04,660 --> 00:39:05,500
It's not accurate.

906
00:39:06,060 --> 00:39:07,420
Mr... Mr. Xing.

907
00:39:07,420 --> 00:39:08,580
There's good news, too.

908
00:39:08,860 --> 00:39:10,060
We've got the plate number

909
00:39:10,060 --> 00:39:10,900
of the motorbike.

910
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:12,340
If we look into it,

911
00:39:12,340 --> 00:39:13,420
we'll find something.

912
00:39:17,980 --> 00:39:19,460
It's much easier to fake a plate

913
00:39:19,460 --> 00:39:20,500
