914
00:39:21,180 --> 00:39:22,300
What good news?

915
00:39:36,180 --> 00:39:39,580
(Bao Chenyan)

916
00:39:44,420 --> 00:39:46,660
(Bao Chenyan)

917
00:39:58,580 --> 00:39:59,700
Hello.

918
00:40:00,540 --> 00:40:01,420
Can you

919
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:03,420
do me a favor?

920
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:43,180
The moon is surrounded by stars

921
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:47,610
I hide my regrets in the dark

922
00:40:48,370 --> 00:40:50,430
You said don't go

923
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:55,970
Because that's where you belong

924
00:40:58,230 --> 00:41:01,790
Wild winds blow across the land

925
00:41:02,250 --> 00:41:06,300
Witnessing the hardships
we've been through

926
00:41:07,010 --> 00:41:09,330
You said don't be afraid

927
00:41:09,330 --> 00:41:13,880
Even though life is always hard

928
00:41:15,030 --> 00:41:16,950
Looking back

929
00:41:16,950 --> 00:41:19,610
My laughters and tears

930
00:41:19,610 --> 00:41:21,510
You've seen them all

931
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:24,210
I've loved, got hurt, and made mistakes

932
00:41:24,210 --> 00:41:26,190
Maybe it's in the past

933
00:41:26,190 --> 00:41:27,750
Still remember

934
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:33,550
The promises I made

935
00:41:34,050 --> 00:41:35,580
Dream about those years

936
00:41:35,580 --> 00:41:38,260
Waking up feeling painful

937
00:41:38,260 --> 00:41:40,250
On those lonely nights

938
00:41:40,250 --> 00:41:42,920
I couldn't sleep

939
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:44,890
Praying for a good ending

940
00:41:44,890 --> 00:41:46,630
All that's left

941
00:41:46,630 --> 00:41:51,730
Is a sigh

942
00:41:58,820 --> 00:42:00,280
How I wish

943
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:07,430
I could see you again
